<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 09:14:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法国干邑白兰地生产商集会呼吁中国对调查采取“开放态度”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/french-cognac-makers-rally-chinas-open-attitude-probe-2024-05-07/</link><description>法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙(Emmanuel Macron)表示，中国总统在贸易争端中持开放态度，中国可能对进口欧盟白兰地征收关税，法国干邑白兰地生产商周二上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 09:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/french-cognac-makers-rally-chinas-open-attitude-probe-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉4月份中国产电动汽车销量同比下降18%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-fall-18-yy-april-2024-05-07/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉4月份销售了62,167辆中国制造的电动汽车，同比下降18%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:50:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-fall-18-yy-april-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>媒体报道西南医院持刀袭击造成2人死亡、21人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/knife-attack-kills-two-wounds-21-southwest-china-hospital-media-reports-2024-05-07/</link><description>据媒体援引警方消息称，周二，中国西南部云南省一家医院发生持刀袭击事件，造成 2 人死亡、21 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/knife-attack-kills-two-wounds-21-southwest-china-hospital-media-reports-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称中金公司今年或将削减至少10%投行人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-may-cut-investment-banking-headcount-by-least-10-this-year-sources-2024-05-07/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，由于资本市场低迷和经济低迷使前景黯淡，中国国际金融公司（中金公司）今年可能会削减至少 10% 的投资银行员工人数。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-cicc-may-cut-investment-banking-headcount-by-least-10-this-year-sources-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车炒作降温，丰田将从混合动力汽车中获得收益提升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-get-an-earnings-lift-hybrids-ev-hype-cools-2024-05-07/</link><description>丰田汽车周三公布年度收益时，预计混合动力车的需求将大幅提振，这表明随着电池电动汽车的炒作降温，这家全球最畅销的汽车制造商将如何受益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-get-an-earnings-lift-hybrids-ev-hype-cools-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>柬埔寨表示，中国资助的新湄公河运河将把通过越南的航运减少70%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-will-cut-shipping-through-vietnam-by-70-with-new-china-funded-2024-05-07/</link><description>柬埔寨副总理告诉路透社，由于中国出资 17 亿美元升级连接湄公河流域和柬埔寨海岸的运河，柬埔寨计划将通过越南港口的航运减少 70%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-will-cut-shipping-through-vietnam-by-70-with-new-china-funded-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>4 月份亚洲股市面临适度的外资流出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-face-modest-foreign-outflows-april-2024-05-07/</link><description>由于美国国债收益率上升，交易员预计美联储将在更长时间内维持高利率以应对通胀压力，4月份主要亚洲市场出现温和的外资流出。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-face-modest-foreign-outflows-april-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本告诉美国拜登的“仇外”言论令人遗憾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-tells-us-that-bidens-xenophobia-comment-is-regrettable-2024-05-07/</link><description>日本政府高级发言人周二表示，美国总统乔·拜登有关“仇外心理”正在扼杀这个亚洲国家经济增长的言论“令人遗憾”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:36:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-tells-us-that-bidens-xenophobia-comment-is-regrettable-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>英国部长表示，在收到黑客报告后，英国已关闭军事数据库</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-has-taken-military-database-offline-after-hack-reports-says-minister-2024-05-07/</link><description>英国一位高级大臣周二表示，据媒体报道，英国国防部使用的数据库遭到中国政府黑客攻击后，英国迅速采取行动，将其下线。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:35:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-has-taken-military-database-offline-after-hack-reports-says-minister-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国三月份出口反弹，但工业订单令人失望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-more-than-expected-march-2024-05-07/</link><description>受美国和中国对德国制造商品强劲需求的提振，德国出口在 3 月份出现反弹，但工业订单令人失望的月份令经济迅速复苏的希望破灭。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:34:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-more-than-expected-march-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国与空客签署谅解备忘录以深化航空合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-signs-mou-with-airbus-deepen-aviation-cooperation-state-media-says-2024-05-07/</link><description>据中国官方媒体新华社周二报道，中国国家规划部门与空中客车公司签署了一份关于深化航空合作的谅解备忘录。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-signs-mou-with-airbus-deepen-aviation-cooperation-state-media-says-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国解除塞尔维亚禽流感风险预警</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-lifts-risk-alert-warning-bird-flu-serbia-2024-05-07/</link><description>中国海关总署周二宣布，中国解除对塞尔维亚禽流感风险预警。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-lifts-risk-alert-warning-bird-flu-serbia-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国 Zeekr 将提前一天在纽约完成 3.675 亿美元的 IPO</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-close-3675-mln-new-york-ipo-one-day-early-source-says-2024-05-07/</link><description>据两位直接了解情况的消息人士透露，中国电动汽车制造商智客智能科技控股有限公司将于周三完成在纽约的首次公开募股 (IPO) 询价，筹集至多 3.675 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-close-3675-mln-new-york-ipo-one-day-early-source-says-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国蔚来转向竞争对手比亚迪为新电动汽车品牌提供动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-turns-rival-byd-power-new-ev-brand-sources-say-2024-05-07/</link><description>三位直接了解此事的消息人士称，中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车已与规模更大的竞争对手比亚迪达成协议，为价格较低的电动汽车品牌采购电池，旨在与特斯拉竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-turns-rival-byd-power-new-ev-brand-sources-say-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>据官方媒体报道，中国习近平和马克龙敦促“政治解决”伊朗核问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-macron-urge-political-settlement-iran-nuclear-issue-state-media-2024-05-07/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平和法国总统马克龙在中国官方媒体周二发表的联合声明中重申致力于推动伊朗核问题的政治解决。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 04:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-macron-urge-political-settlement-iran-nuclear-issue-state-media-2024-05-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>